data.description: Come home to spanning mountain and valley views from every vantage point, inside and out! This home has been beautifully renovated and upgraded throughout.  With LVP flooring in most living areas, the design through the home is cohesive and inviting.  Warm up by the gorgeous fireplace with rock surround as a centerpiece to the great room.  This home has fresh paint, granite countertops, gorgeous cabinetry, and room to stretch your legs! Bring your horse and bring your toys to clean country living. The landscape is lush and mature, so no waiting on the trees to grow.  The fourth bedroom does not have a closet, but is labeled as such by the assessor.
